name: RYN_WHT_HYSTERECTOMY_SCRN
description: Stores data for Ryan White CAREWare Hysterectomy screenings.

columns.name: REGISTRY_DATA_ID
columns.description: The unique identifier (.1 item) for the registry data record.

columns.name: LINE
columns.description: The line number for the information associated with this record. Multiple pieces of information can be associated with this record.

columns.name: RW_HYSTER_DATE
columns.description: Date of the Hysterectomy (non-dysplasia/non-malignant indic.) screening.

columns.name: RW_HYST_SCORE
columns.description: The numerical score of the Hysterectomy screening.

columns.name: RW_HYSTERECTOMY_CMT
columns.description: The comments for the Hysterectomy screening.
